my meme

Juice Wrld is my favorite rapper and I started listening to his songs when I was 15 years old. His music has been an inspiration to me ever since. His lyrics were so honest and real, and I felt like he understood what I was going through. Its heartbreaking that he passed away at such a young age, but I will always cherish the memories I have of listening to his music and the impact it has had on my life. Juice Wrld was an American rapper, singer, and songwriter who rose to fame with his hit songs Lucid Dreams and All Girls Are the Same. He was known for his unique style of music, which combined elements of hip-hop, rock, and emo. Unfortunately, Juice Wrld passed away at a young age due to a drug overdose in December 2019. His music continues to inspire and impact fans around the world.

install.packages("magick")
library(magick)
library(tidyverse)

meme <- image_read("https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/JuiceWRLD_NME_AFord-6601-696x442.jpg")%>%
  image_append(image_scale(500)) %>% #size change
  image_annotate("Juice Wrld", size = 50, gravity = "north", color = "purple") %>% #top
  image_annotate("Legends Never Die", size = 50, gravity = "south", color = "purple") #bottom

blank <- image_blank(650,50,"green")

finalmeme <- image_append(c(meme, blank), stack = TRUE)#stacking

finalmeme#final meme

image_write(finalmeme,"My_meme.png")

My animated GIF

This Tom and Jerry GIF brings back so many fond memories for me. It was my favorite cartoon when I was growing up, and I used to watch it every chance I got. I loved the silly and mischievous antics of Tom the cat and Jerry the mouse, and their endless pursuit of each other always had me in stitches. Even now, as an adult, I still enjoy watching old episodes of the show and reliving those happy childhood memories. 

library(magick)
taj1 <- image_scale(image_read("https://www.redwolf.in/image/cache/catalog/stickers/tom-and-jerry-chase-sticker-india-438x438.png"))
taj2 <- image_scale(image_read("https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSBFuA81KJPrw09GuKWDj_waxvLrzlcQoc3msXgB_QooQoWu9kUFKBsVZUnBH1LwQexwKk&usqp=CAU"))

animation <- image_resize(c(taj1,taj2),"500X500!")%>%
  
  image_background("white") %>%
  image_morph(frames = 16) %>%
  image_animate(optimize = TRUE) %>% 
  image_annotate("Tom and Jerry", size =35, gravity = "north",)
